Syrian Vice-President Farouk al-Sharaa, right, meets on Wednesday, Jan. 31, 2007 with Sheikh Harith Al-Dhari, head of the influential Sunni Association of Muslim scholars in Iraq, for talks on the spiraling violence in Iraq.(AP Photo Bassem Tellawi).
